Description: Ostracon, half a fragment of the body of a pale-red pottery vessel, the exterior is covered with a light-brown slip and remains of six lines of black-painted demotic text. The other half is EA66325.
Curator's comments: Being studied for publication by Bryan Kraemer. Cemeteries and Osireion Excavations Group
